videos.description: Anthony Walker drives to the rim for such a big dunk that he loses a shoe in the process.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Walker jumps out of his shoe on big dunk) 2020/1/25

videos.headline: Walker jumps out of his shoe on big dunk

videos.description: Armando Bacot gets the ball and dunks it before the buzzer goes off, giving North Carolina a 51-27 lead over Miami.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bacot throws it down to beat the 1st-half horn) 2020/1/25

videos.headline: Bacot throws it down to beat the 1st-half horn

videos.description: Brandon Robinson and Armando Bacot help lift North Carolina past Miami. It's Roy Williams' 880th victory, which gives him sole possession of fourth on college basketball's men's Division I all-time wins list.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Williams passes Dean Smith on wins list as UNC snaps 5-game skid) 2020/1/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams passes Dean Smith on wins list as UNC snaps 5-game skid
